ing that links the X-ray and the gamma-ray\nenergy to the prompt spectral peak energy of BOTH long and short GRBs:\nE_{X,iso}\\propto E_{gamma,iso}^{1.00\\pm 0.06}/E_{pk}^{0.60\\pm 0.10}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Mar 2012 21:28:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Oct 2012 14:41:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
