e is proven, if the variable mass decays to zero sufficiently fast.\nThe strategy is based on a path measure argument.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Mar 2012 08:52:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-03-07"}
